reviewText:

My husband watched it twice....he loved it!
Felioe on stage is like watching one of your funny family members or best friends up there.  You can't help but laugh and smile the whole time.  He's a likeable guy and hilarious.  Love the guy!
Felipe Esparza came at me out of nowhere.  Felipe was just straight hilarious.  You will not go wrong with this DVD.

One of the most funny and most real comic routines by this deserving winner of Last Comic Standing.
Viva Felipe!!!

This guy brings some real-life jokes to the stage!
He reminds me a little of George Lopez as he animates and imitates some of the cultural traditions of being Mexican.
But he is definitely no George Lopez knock-off...He adds a unique spin to his stand up - keeping it real and hella funny.
Luv it!
Love it!
all I can say is jajajajajajajajajaj....

If laughter is medicine Felipe is the type you need a prescription for (non generic)
ok at best
Hilarious.

I originally saw this on Netflix streaming and I enjoyed it so much I made sure to purchase it because Netflix is always adding/dropping from their streaming list. One might say that the Mexican jokes get a little old, but I think that Felipe does it right and I hope to see more of him in the future.
Great dvd! Had me laughing the whole time. Received it in a great time and good condition!

Get ready to laugh! Especially if you are hispanic or speak spanish. Not a lot of spanish in it at all, but he does throw in the occasional naughty word lol!  Bought  it for a friends birthday goody bag. Great price, well worth the five dollars. Was well packaged and arrived undamaged.

Saw this dude on Showtime after hearing his name in a lot of Gabriel Iglesias' bits. He is hilarious but more subtle than fluffy and he is one of my favorite comedians.
I give him five stars he's jokes make laugh and i think he's hot and would love to see his show.
I love stand up comedians and this is one of the funniest ones! And without a lot of cussing, which is often unnecessary.
Loved the DVD! It was way too funny! Recommend to anyone who likes Gabriel Englesias or other comedians like him, Absolutely!
